OL,6,GServices including Freeview in the UK
OL,7,Gand Saorview in Ireland won't be
OL,8,Gexpected to switch off at the end of
OL,9,Gthe decade.
OL,11,FAfter four weeks of negotiation,
OL,12,Fdelegates at the World
OL,13,FRadiocommunications Conference (WRC-
OL,14,F23) opted to safeguard UHF frequencies
OL,15,Ffor terrestrial TV in Europe.
