OL,4,Cedge
OL,6,FThe WRC-23 was organised by the ITU,
OL,7,Fan executive agency of the United
OL,8,FNations responsible for the global
OL,9,Fcoordination of radio frequency
OL,10,Fspectrum. It took place in Dubai, but
OL,11,Fwas rather overshadowed by COP28
OL,12,Ftaking place at the same time.
OL,14,FTerrestrial TV services will continue
OL,15,Fto enjoy primary use of the 470 ` 694
OL,16,FMHz frequency band and won't need to
OL,17,Fcome to an abrupt end in 2030.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/22
