OL,4,Cedge
OL,6,FAt present, all digital terrestrial TV
OL,7,Fmultiplexes look set to run until 2034
OL,8,Fonly.
OL,10,FCash-strapped Public Service
OL,11,FBroadcasters haven't come out in
OL,12,Fsupport of retaining terrestrial TV.
OL,13,FThere is little to no investment in
OL,14,Fupgrading more services to the newer
OL,15,FDVB-T2 standard, let alone to HEVC
OL,16,Fencoding.
OL,18,FThe UK, which once led with DVB-T2
OL,19,Fintroduction, has now fallen way
OL,20,Fbehind.
