OL,6,FIn fact the multiplex licence for the
OL,7,FFreeview HD multiplex (PSB3) is the
OL,8,Fonly licence that hasn't been renewed
OL,9,Fand where the licence holder ` the BBC
OL,10,F` has been on the record as being
OL,11,Freluctant to commit to a licence
OL,12,Frenewal when the DCMS consulted on
OL,13,Flicence renewals.
OL,15,FWhat investment there is, is flowing
OL,16,Finto the development of streaming
OL,17,Fservice Freely.
OL,19,FElsewhere in Europe, the Republic of
OL,20,FIreland is also gearing up to launch a
OL,21,Fstreaming-based solution to succeed
OL,22,Fthe DTT platform Saorview.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/22
