OL,6,FBut in France, there's talk of
OL,7,Fupgrading more terrestrial TV services
OL,8,Fto 4K UHD.
OL,10,FIn Croatia, the Czech Republic,
OL,11,FFinland, France, Germany, Italy and
OL,12,FSpain, 5G Broadcast trials have taken
OL,13,Fplace, with many seeing the technology
OL,14,Fas the future universal free platform
OL,15,Ffor Public Service Media.
