OL,4,Cedge
OL,6,F5G Broadcast works on mobile devices,
OL,7,Fincluding potential 5G-capatible TVs,
OL,8,Fwithout the need for a SIM card. It
OL,9,Fdoes not require a subscription and
OL,10,Fdata consumption won't count towards
OL,11,Fany data allowance. It can be used at
OL,12,Fhome and on the move.
OL,14,FThe WRC-23 decision will allow
OL,15,Findividual countries to now press on
OL,16,Fwith developing free-to-air TV how
OL,17,Fthey see fit without the axe having to
OL,18,Ffall in 2030.
