OL,6,FIn the UK, it seems digital
OL,7,Fterrestrial TV will be allowed to have
OL,8,Fa natural death at some point in the
OL,9,Fnext decade, likely after 2034, given
OL,10,Fthe general apathy on the matter.
OL,12,FNo. The number of broadband-only TV
OL,13,Fhomes in the UK is currently around
OL,14,F15%.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G8/22
