OL,3,CTerrestrial TV saved from 2030 cliff
OL,4,Cedge
OL,6,FThat's still high given streaming TV
OL,7,Fplatforms like Sky Stream and VM
OL,8,FStream have only been around for a
OL,9,Fshort time, and prior to that being a
OL,10,Fbroadband-only TV user would have
OL,11,Finvolved navigating in and out of
OL,12,Fvarious apps to access content,
OL,13,Finstead of having them all in one
OL,14,Fplace.
OL,16,FMillions more of course are hybrid,
OL,17,Fbut still rely on a terrestrial, cable
OL,18,For satellite service for reception of
OL,19,Fkey services.
