OL,3,CTerrestrial TV saved from 2030 cliff
OL,4,Cedge
OL,6,FLinear TV use is declining. But
OL,7,FOfcom's analysis on the matter earlier
OL,8,Fthis year showed channels like BBC One
OL,9,Fand ITV 1 still benefit from large
OL,10,Faudiences for major news, sports and
OL,11,Fcultural events.
OL,13,FSo there will need to be some way of
OL,14,Faccessing linear or live TV in the
OL,15,Ffuture, even if it's just a much
OL,16,Fsmaller group of main channels only.
OL,17,FPerhaps we'll end up with five main
OL,18,Fchannels again.
OL,20,FA record of what the WRC-23 has
OL,21,Fdecided are found in a document called
OL,22,Fthe "Provisional Final Acts".
