OL,6,FIt confirms that while terrestrial TV
OL,7,Fwill continue to enjoy primary use of
OL,8,Fthe UHF TV spectrum, a secondary
OL,9,Fallocation for mobile will exist in
OL,10,Fmost European countries including the
OL,11,FUK and Ireland.
OL,13,FBut any mobile service will have to
OL,14,Fplay second fiddle to broadcasting.
