OL,6,FThe WRC-23 says "For the protection of
OL,7,Fthe broadcasting service, stations in
OL,8,Fthe mobile service shall not create a
OL,9,Ffield strength for more than 1% of the
OL,10,Ftime at the highest of the clutter
OL,11,Fheight or 10m above ground level at
OL,12,Fthe border of the territory of any
OL,13,Fother administration that exceeds the
OL,14,Ffield strength value as calculated
OL,15,Fusing S 4.1.3.2 of Annex 2 to the GE06
OL,16,FAgreement with regard to allowance for
OL,17,Fmultiple interference."
