OL,6,FHowever, in countries where
OL,7,Fterrestrial TV has already been wound
OL,8,Fdown (e.g., Switzerland, with the
OL,9,Fexception of a small number of near-
OL,10,Fborder transmitters retransmitting
OL,11,FSwiss networks for the benefit of
OL,12,Fcross-border cable networks), this
OL,13,Fallocation will be of interest. And it
OL,14,Fmay be of interest even in the UK.
