OL,3,CTerrestrial TV saved from 2030 cliff
OL,4,Cedge
OL,6,FThe UK doesn't appear to be interested
OL,7,Fin 5G Broadcast, so the UK's mobile
OL,8,Foperators, of which all but one are
OL,9,Falso major players in the fixed-line
OL,10,Fbroadband market (two also have their
OL,11,Fown TV platform and have a vested
OL,12,Finterest in shutting DTT), may now
OL,13,Fstart lobbying to remove terrestrial
OL,14,FTV sooner.
OL,16,FIn the UK, the future direction of
OL,17,Ftravel in terms of broadcasting is to
OL,18,Fensure all homes have universal access
OL,19,Fto full fibre fixed line broadband.
