OL,3,CTerrestrial TV saved from 2030 cliff
OL,4,Cedge
OL,6,FWith three companies ` BT/EE, Vodafone
OL,7,Fand Virgin Media O2 ` having dominance
OL,8,Fin both mobile and fixed line
OL,9,Fbroadband, there are calls for less
OL,10,Fwell-off homes to gain broader access
OL,11,Fto social tariffs, which in the future
OL,12,Fwill ensure they can access basic TV
OL,13,Fservices.
OL,15,FThe three satellites that provide the
OL,16,FUK and Ireland with direct-to-home
OL,17,Fsatellite from Sky and Freesat ` Astra
OL,18,F2E, 2F and 2G ` all reach end of life
OL,19,Fbefore the end of this decade. They're
OL,20,Foperated by Luxembourg's SES.
