OL,3,CTerrestrial TV saved from 2030 cliff
OL,4,Cedge
OL,6,FSES would need a firm commitment from
OL,7,Fa variety of UK broadcasters to
OL,8,Fjustify sending up more satellites for
OL,9,Fanother 15 years to keep satellite TV
OL,10,Frunning in its current form. This
OL,11,Fappears unlikely.
OL,13,FBig events like the recent Coronation
OL,14,Fand Eurovision wouldn't be possible
OL,15,Fwithout the use of spare UHF
OL,16,Ffrequencies for Programme Making. And
OL,17,FPMSE will continue to be able to use
OL,18,Fthe spectrum on a secondary basis
OL,19,Fgoing forward in the UK, Ireland and
OL,20,Fnumerous other countries across ITU
OL,21,FRegion 1.
