OL,6,FThis isn't a surprise. Mobile industry
OL,7,Flobbyist GSMA has long taken an
OL,8,Finterest in the development of digital
OL,9,Fterrestrial TV in the region,
OL,10,Fconcluding back in 2015 that the
OL,11,Fcountries don't need all that spectrum
OL,12,Ffor TV. And the mobile industry has
OL,13,Fthat spectrum.
OL,15,FSpain and Italy will not have a
OL,16,Fsecondary allocation for mobile in the
OL,17,FUHF TV band.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G18/22
