OL,3,CTerrestrial TV saved from 2030 cliff
OL,4,Cedge
OL,6,FBoth countries are intense users of
OL,7,Fthe UHF band for digital terrestrial
OL,8,FTV with Italy continuing on its
OL,9,Froadmap to switch to HEVC encoding and
OL,10,Fadd more HD channels. Spain has been
OL,11,Ftesting 4K and even 8K UHD.
OL,13,FIn Germany, Austria, Denmark, Estonia,
OL,14,FLiechtenstein, Serbia and Switzerland,
OL,15,Fthe bottom of the UHF band (470 ` 494
OL,16,FMHz) can also be used by wind profiler
OL,17,Fradars.
